README.textile

Awesome

   A curated list of amazingly awesome
   [http://textpattern.com/]Textpattern CMS plugins, resources and shiny
   things.

   This list is for the latest version of Textpattern (v4.6.x). For
   Textpattern v4.5.x see the
   [https://github.com/drmonkeyninja/awesome-textpattern/tree/txp-4.5]txp-
   4.5 branch.

Contributing

   This list is for the community and curated by it, so please contribute.
   See
   [https://github.com/drmonkeyninja/awesome-textpattern/blob/master/CONTR
   IBUTING.textile]CONTRIBUTING for details.

