Plugins

Admin

     * [https://github.com/ClaireBrione/cbe_frontauth]cbe_frontauth -
       Manage backend connections from frontend and protect content from
       non-logged in users.
     * [https://github.com/hakjoon/hak_tinymce]hak_tinymce - TinyMCE
       integration for Textpattern.
     * [https://github.com/jbach/jbx_multiple_image_upload]jbx_multiple_im
       age_upload - Multiple image upload.
     * [https://github.com/gocom/rah_privileges]rah_privileges - Configure
       Textpattern's admin-side user-group privileges through the
       Preferences panel.
     * [https://github.com/spiffin/spf_codemirror]spf_codemirror -
       CodeMirror syntax-highlighting and Emmet code-completion for Pages,
       Forms, Styles, etc.
     * [https://github.com/spiffin/spf_js]spf_js - JavaScript management
       (similar to Presentation -> Styles).
     * [https://github.com/Sacripant/tom_image_grid]tom_image_grid -
       Provides a more compact grid interface for the image admin panel.
     * [https://github.com/trenc/yab_copy_to_new]yab_copy_to_new - Allows
       for easy copying of articles from the Write panel.

Comments

     * [https://github.com/drmonkeyninja/arc_admin_comment_preview]arc_adm
       in_comment_preview - Adds a comment preview to admin.
     * [https://github.com/juanjonavarro/jnm_recent_comments_unique]jnm_re
       cent_comments_unique - Show latest comments.
     * [https://github.com/gocom/rah_comments]rah_comments - Paginated
       article comments.
     * [https://github.com/gocom/rah_comment_spam]rah_comment_spam -
       Comment anti-spam plugin.

Content

     * [https://github.com/gerhard/glz_custom_fields]glz_custom_fields -
       Unlimited custom fields.
     * [https://github.com/Bloke/smd_tags]smd_tags - Unlimited, structured
       taxonomy across content types.

Embedding

     * [https://github.com/drmonkeyninja/arc_vimeo]arc_vimeo - Easily
       embed Vimeo videos.
     * [https://github.com/drmonkeyninja/arc_youtube]arc_youtube - Easily
       embed YouTube videos.
     * [https://github.com/NicolasGraph/oui_embed]oui_embed - Embed any
       information from any web page using
       [https://github.com/oscarotero/Embed]Embed.
     * [https://github.com/NicolasGraph/oui_instagram]oui_instagram -
       Easily embed Instagram recent images galleries.
     * [https://github.com/NicolasGraph/oui_player]oui_player - Easily
       embed customizable players from a growing providers list.

Forms

     * [https://github.com/Bloke/zem_contact_reborn]zem_contact_reborn -
       Contact forms.

Images

     * [https://github.com/Bloke/smd_imagery]smd_imagery - Article images
       management.
     * [https://github.com/Bloke/smd_thumbnail]smd_thumbnail - Multiple
       image thumbnails of arbitrary dimensions.

Navigation

     * [http://www.greatoceanmedia.com.au/txp/?plugin=adi_menu]adi_menu -
       Section hierarchy, section menu and breadcrumb trail.
     * [https://github.com/etc-plugins/etc_pagination]etc_pagination -
       Paginate everything.
     * [https://github.com/Bloke/smd_horizon]smd_horizon - Advanced
       next/previous links.

Performance

     * [http://textpattern.org.ua/plugins/aks_cache]aks_cache - Partially
       cache parts of a Textpattern template via tags.
     * [https://github.com/netcarver/asy_jpcache]asy_jpcache - Full page
       caching.
     * [https://github.com/etc-plugins/etc_cache]etc_cache - Events-driven
       cache solution for Textpattern CMS.
     * [https://github.com/gocom/rah_cache]rah_cache - Cache dynamic pages
       as flat files.
     * [https://github.com/gocom/rah_cache_minify]rah_cache_minify - HTML
       compressor module for rah_cache plugin.
     * [https://github.com/gocom/rah_memcached]rah_memcached - Store parts
       of Textpattern templates in [http://memcached.org/]Memcached.
     * [https://vanmelick.com/txp/rvm_css.php?help]rvm_css - Static CSS
       caching.

SEO

     * [https://github.com/drmonkeyninja/arc_meta]arc_meta - Meta tags to
       improve site SEO and social marketing.
     * [https://github.com/drmonkeyninja/arc_redirect]arc_redirect - URL
       redirect plugin.
     * [https://github.com/gocom/rah_sitemap]rah_sitemap - XML sitemap
       generator.
     * [https://github.com/wcz-txp/Unicode-url-for-Textpattern]wcz_utf8_ur
       l - UTF-8 permlinks instead of transliterated ones.

Social

   Plugins that add social features to Textpattern.
     * [https://github.com/drmonkeyninja/arc_social_share]arc_social_share
       - Social bookmarking.
     * [https://github.com/cara-tm/pat_article_social]pat_article_social -
       Social bookmarking with share counts.
     * [https://github.com/drmonkeyninja/TXP-Tweet]TXP Tweet -
       Twitter-Textpattern integration.

Miscellaneous

     * [https://github.com/brachycera/fly_excerpt]fly_excerpt - Truncate
       the article excerpt.
     * [https://github.com/NicolasGraph/oui_cookie]oui_cookie - Set, read,
       reset or delete cookies manually or through URL variables.
     * [https://github.com/NicolasGraph/oui_quote]oui_quote - Pull and
       display a quote from [http://quotesondesign.com/]Quotes on design,
       [https://theysaidso.com/]They said so,
       [http://evene.lefigaro.fr/citations]Le figaro or
       [http://dicocitations.lemonde.fr/citations-mot-monde.php]Le Monde.
     * [https://github.com/cara-tm/pat_if_amp]pat_if_amp - Serve Google's
       Accelerated Mobile Pages (AMP) in Textpattern.
     * [https://github.com/cara-tm/pat_eu_cookies_law]pat_eu_cookies_law -
       EU Cookie Law compliance: A Textpattern CMS plugin for third-party
       cookies.
     * [https://github.com/gocom/rah_backup]rah_backup - Takes backups
       from Textpattern CMS installations.
     * [https://github.com/NicolasGraph/rah_flat]rah_flat - Edit
       Textpattern's database contents and page templates as flat files.
     * [https://github.com/gocom/rah_terminal]rah_terminal - Terminal
       interface emulator.
     * [https://vanmelick.com/txp/rvm_maintenance.php?help]rvm_maintenance
       - Shows a maintenance page to all visitors who are not logged in on
       the admin side.
     * [http://stefdawson.com/sw/plugins/smd_if]smd_if - A generic `if
       condition' tester.
     * [https://github.com/gocom/textpattern-installer]textpattern-install
       er - Textpattern plugin and theme installer for Composer.
     * [https://github.com/wcz-txp/upm_pending_notify]upm_pending_notify -
       Pending article notifications.

Plugin Development

     * [https://github.com/Bloke/ied_plugin_composer]ied_plugin_composer -
       Create, publish and edit plugins.
     * [https://github.com/gocom/MassPlugCompiler]MassPlugCompiler -
       Compiles Textpattern's plugin installer packages from separate
       source files.
     * [https://github.com/textpattern/textpattern-plugin-template]Plugin
       template repo - A starter package for plugin developers.

Themes

Back-end

     * [http://design-patterns.textpattern.io/docs/]Hive theme design
       patterns - Core designer guidelines for themes and plugins
       developers.
     * [https://github.com/textpattern/textpattern-jquery-ui-theme]jQuery
       UI theme repo - The jQuery UI theme used within the Textpattern
       admin-side.

Front-end

     * [https://github.com/textpattern/textpattern-default-theme]Default
       theme repo - The theme that ships as standard with Textpattern CMS.

Resources

   Various resources, such as books, websites and articles, for improving
   your Textpattern skills and knowledge.

Official resources

     * [http://textpattern.com/]Official website - Download link, features
       description and informations the CMS.
     * [http://docs.textpattern.io/]Textpattern Documentation - The
       textpattern user guidelines.

Web development software integration

     * [https://github.com/philwareham/Textpattern-for-Panic-Coda]Textpatt
       ern for Panic Coda - Handy elements for use with Panic Coda 2 on a
       Mac.

